metadata.name: An Embryo in Development
metadata.description:
In this striking image, an AI trained on the works of Wassily Kandinsky interprets the phrase: "An Embryo in Development."   

Notable features include the various character-like notations, some of which look like musical notes, dotted throughout the image. These beautifully cryptic scripts may represent the AI's interpretation of the molecular and genetic basis of life.
